Loops in C++:
    1.  for loop
    2.  while loop
    3.  do-while loop:
            do{
                //do some work
            }while(condition);
            
            ->  Work gets done atleast once.

Two Important terms in respect of Break Statement
    1.  Break : To exit from a loop.
    2.  Continue:   To skip an iteration.
            ->  The statements after continue gets skipped.
                
